# L'Atelier - Timeless Desserts

Artisanal French patisserie website showcasing handcrafted desserts. Emphasis on timeless quality, subtle animations, and fast performance.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Astro 5.x (static HTML generation, 0 JS by default)
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4.x (utility-first)
- **Image Optimization**: astro:assets + Sharp (WebP/AVIF, responsive srcset)
- **Animations**: Native CSS + Intersection Observer (fade-in, parallax)
- **Fonts**: Inter (body), Cormorant Garamond (headings), Rigot (display/branding)
- **Deployment**: Vercel (Edge CDN)

