## Design Conventions

- **Typography**: Rigot for h1 and branding, Cormorant Garamond for h2-h6
- **Buttons**: Accent (`bg-accent text-white`) with 90% opacity hover
- **Links**: Accent text with warm hover (`text-accent hover:text-accent-warm`)
- **Sections**: Alternate between beige background and white for visual rhythm
- **CTA Sections**: Use `bg-secondary` (gris clair) background
- **Footer**: Secondary background with accent borders

## File Naming

- **Components**: PascalCase (`Header.astro`)
- **Pages**: kebab-case (`about.astro`)
- **Images**: kebab-case (`wedding-cake.jpg`)
- **CSS**: global.css for theme, scoped styles in components

## Performance Optimizations

- Images auto-converted to WebP/AVIF via Sharp
- Critical CSS inlined
- Fonts preloaded (Inter, Cormorant Garamond)
- Lazy loading for below-fold images
- View Transitions API for smooth navigation

## Internationalization

- **Languages**: English (default), Spanish, French
- **Config**: `src/i18n/ui.ts` for translations
- **Routing**: Prefix for non-default locales (/es/, /fr/)

